msgid "Using CSRF Protection in the Login Form"
msgstr ""

#: ../../cookbook/security/csrf_in_login_form.rst:7
msgid ""
"When using a login form, you should make sure that you are protected against"
" CSRF (`Cross-site request forgery`_). The Security component already has "
"built-in support for CSRF. In this article you'll learn how you can use it "
"in your login form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../cookbook/security/csrf_in_login_form.rst:13
msgid ""
"Login CSRF attacks are a bit less well-known. See `Forging Login Requests`_ "
"if you're curious about more details."
msgstr ""

